lead_paragraph: Mix Diskerud scored the eventual game winner in the 63rd minute and NYCFC beat the Chicago Fire 4-3 on Sunday in a wild affair in the MLS season opener for both sides.

headline.print_headline: NYCFC Tops Chicago 4-3 in Wild MLS Opener
